[07:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'IC Lora actually are. Let\'s start with the basics. Test one, single character consistency. Here, I\'m using only one character reference and asking the model to generate different camera angles,'

[07:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'viewpoints, [music] and slightly different poses. Let\'s look at the results. In most cases, the overall appearance of the character remains fairly consistent. The hairstyle, outfit, and major visual features are preserved.'

